<h2>Why Inghams? Meet the experts!</h2>
<p>For over 80 years, Inghams have shared our wealth of knowledge with skiers and snowboarders and have tailored our holidays to ensure that what we offer, is perfect for our guests. How do we do this? By ensuring that our teams both overseas and in our UK head office are passionate about the slopes whatever you’ve got on your feet! As the ski &amp; snowboard experts we’re proud of this expertise and we’re eager to get you on the snow to experience it for yourselves year in, year out <br /><br /></p>
